Title: HumanLungCancerV3
Description: Vectra 3 multiplex immunohistochemistry (mIHC) dataset of non-small cell lung cancer tissue with 1,604,786 cells from 761 total images from 153 patients

Title: HumanOvarianCancerVP
Description: Vectra Polaris multiplex immunohistochemistry (mIHC) dataset from a tumor microarray of cancerous ovarian tissue with 1,610,431 cells from 132 total images from 132 patients
